    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/575340/extras/f1937ee3d4c6bbeb0a71ecea3e9de154.avif?t=1561735338\" width=616 height=105 /></span><br>Chessaria提供前所未有的经典国际象棋战斗，配上史诗般的奇幻任务。挑战您的战术技能，对抗电脑对手，为Chessaria的未来而战。体验具有战术深度，广度和挑战的策略游戏，体验前所未有的的玩法：国际象棋，策略设置和故事任务的原创组合。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事</strong></h2>经过一千年的和平与繁荣后，精灵城市西尔弗兰被北方的一条龙烧成了灰烬。勇敢的勇士将在Chessaria的世界踏上传奇的旅程，以寻求正义并揭开袭击背后的真相...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/575340/extras/344525bbb1213d1ec1dfe23612edb72a.poster.avif?t=1561735338\" width=616 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/575340/extras/344525bbb1213d1ec1dfe23612edb72a.webm?t=1561735338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/575340/extras/344525bbb1213d1ec1dfe23612edb72a.mp4?t=1561735338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特点</strong></h2><br>♟ <strong>任务型的棋类游戏</strong><br> - <strong>冒险模式：</strong>在单人战役的100个关卡中，战斗并解决难题（+20小时）。<br> - <strong>快速游戏：</strong>在多人游戏或对抗电脑A.I，享受经典国际象棋和国际象棋变体。<br> - <strong>在线多人游戏：</strong>以在线战斗的方式，跟你Steam的朋友对战。<br>♟ <strong>下一代人工智能</strong><br> - 挑战新一代的人工智能（2800+ ELO），可实现统治，渗透，暗杀等任务。<br>♟ <strong>一个梦幻的世界</strong><br> - 与3个可玩的军队（高等精灵，黑暗精灵和兽人）对战。<br> - 带领六位英雄对战有挑战性的BOSS，这将测试您的战术技巧。<br> - 享受由英国作曲家本·罗尔斯（Ben Rawles）创作的情感配乐。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/575340/extras/709c583ff51575568b4b77c5655503da.poster.avif?t=1561735338\" width=616 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/575340/extras/709c583ff51575568b4b77c5655503da.webm?t=1561735338\" type=\"video/webm; code